= Installing HackingParty-Www =

== Requirements ==

-- As root ;) -- 
First install requirement distribution packages :

    apt-get install rubygems1.8

Then install ruby-specific packages

    gem install dm-core >= 1.0.2
    gem install dm-migrations >= 1.0.2
    gem install dm-sqlite-adapter >= 1.0.2

    gem install sinatra >= 1.1.3
    gem install shotgun >= 0.9
    gem install haml >= 3.0.25
    gem install thin >=

